@node Agraiments "AmiMSX Emulator."

@{fg highlight}    Greetings:
@{fg text}    ----------

    I wish to greet all the following people for their help in the
developement of the MSX2 emulator:

 - Manuel Hiniesta for explaining me all MSX2 hardware.

